        Parameters:
        client - Interface to the UI.
        server - Interface to the microscope.
        frame - The frame in which the fine configuration is displayed.
        configuration - The position configuration which positions should be fine configured.
        focusDevice - The focus device for which the focus value should be stored, or null if focus device value should not be stored.
        stageDevice - The stage device which should be used to change the position.
        forceNewConfiguration - True, if a new path should be generated, even if the old path is still valid. Remark, that if the path is not valid, a new one will be constructed anyway.
